<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
	<meta charset="UTF-8"/>
	<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
	<title>기업 회원가입</title>
	<link
			rel="stylesheet"
			href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/4.7.0/css/font-awesome.min.css"
	/>
	<script src="https://ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/jquery/3.7.1/jquery.min.js"></script>
	<link
			href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css"
			rel="stylesheet"
	/>
	<script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
	<link
			rel="stylesheet"
			href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.5.1/css/all.min.css"
	/>

	<link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/com-save-form.css"/>
	<link
			href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Noto+Sans+KR&display=swap"
			rel="stylesheet"
	/>
</head>

<!-- nav -->
{{> layout/header}}

<!-- main -->
<form action="/join" method="post">
	<div class="felx-box">
		<div class="form-box">
			<div class="save">기업 회원가입</div>

			<div>
				<div class="input-header">기업명</div>
				<input type="text" placeholder="기업명을 입력해주세요"/>
			</div>

			<div>
				<div class="input-header">산업 선택</div>
				<select id="gieob" name="gieob" class="select-box">
					<option selected>산업을 선택해주세요</option>
					<option value="apple">IT, 콘텐츠</option>
					<option value="banana">판매, 유통</option>
					<option value="cherry">제조</option>
					<option value="grape">기타 서비스업</option>
					<option value="cherry">전문, 과학기술</option>
					<option value="cherry">금융</option>
					<option value="cherry">교육</option>
					<option value="cherry">예술, 스포츠, 여가</option>
					<option value="cherry">물류, 운송</option>
					<option value="cherry">부동산</option>
					<option value="cherry">게임</option>
					<option value="cherry">보건, 사회복지</option>
					<option value="cherry">건설</option>
					<option value="cherry">사업지원</option>
					<option value="cherry">숙박, 음식점</option>
					<option value="cherry">상수도, 환경</option>
					<option value="cherry">농림어업</option>
					<option value="cherry">공공행정, 국방</option>
					<option value="cherry">전기, 가스</option>
					<option value="cherry">가사, 가정</option>
					<option value="cherry">국제, 외국기관</option>
				</select>
			</div>

			<div>
				<div class="input-header">아이디</div>
				<div class="input-box">
					<input type="text" placeholder="아이디를 입력해주세요"/>
					<div class="button-box">
						<button type="button" class="check-box">중복확인</button>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>

			<div>
				<div class="input-header">이메일</div>
				<input type="text" placeholder="이메일을 입력해주세요"/>
			</div>

			<div>
				<div class="input-header">휴대전화</div>
				<input type="text" placeholder="휴대전화를 입력해주세요"/>
			</div>

			<div>
				<div class="input-header">비밀번호</div>
				<input type="text" placeholder="비밀번호를 입력해주세요"/>
				<div class="input-header">비밀번호확인</div>
				<input type="text" placeholder="비밀번호를 재입력해주세요"/>
				<div class="checkpwd">
					영문 대소문자, 숫자, 특수문자를 3가지 이상으로 조합해 8자
					이상 16자 이하로 입력해주세요.
				</div>
			</div>

			<div class="save-box">
				<button class="save-btn">가입하기</button>
			</div>
		</div>

	</div>
</form>

<!-- footer -->
{{> layout/footer}}